4193.title: Yo! MTV Raps Presents AJ Tracey...
4193.description: ... 1 On 1. Snoochie Shy chats to rap superstar AJ Tracey about new music, future plans, and his mum! Plus he answers questions sent in by fans, and goes 1 To 1 with Snoochie in a game of basketball!
